ELEVATOR LIFT

Elevators are located all over the place, especially in highrises. Using  
the elevator is quite simple (contrary to popular belief)  
  
When ^Winside^n elevator:  
^c< 10P 10M > look panel^n 
lists all the buttons and shows your current floor.  
^c< 10P 10M > push <button>^n
Where <button> is one of the buttons on the panel.  
When ^Woutside^n elevator:  
^c< 10P 10M > look panel^n
Displays the current floor the elevator is at.  
^c< 10P 10M > push button^n
Calls elevator to your floor.

